headline : Erwin Wurm Exhibition in Wolfsburg
text : \r\nThe art of Austrian sculptor Erwin wurm takes everyday objects out of context and shows them from a whole new perspective. Although humor plays an important role in these works, they often reveal some bitter truths. A comprehensive exhibition in the German city of Wolfsburg shows Wurm's sculptures and installations.\r\n
